A simple keylogger, developed for XMonad screencasting.

To build:
  $ ./bootstrap.sh
  $ ./configure
  $ make

To run:
  $ cd src
  # ./keylog [-k /dev/input/eventX] [-m /dev/input/eventY] [-s keymap.txt]

To find keyboard and mouse device:
  $ grep "mouse\|sysrq" /proc/bus/input/devices

To create a custom keymap:
  $ cd src
  $ rm keymap.txt
  $ make keymap.txt
  # showkey
  $ vi keymap.txt

